Class CircularLinkedList

java.lang.Object
clinic.cs213project3.model.util.CircularLinkedList
public class CircularLinkedList extends Object
The implementation of a circular linked list of Technician objects. This list is used to assign technicians to new clinic appointments.
Author:
Aarush Desai
